title: Blac Chyna Publicly DRAGS 'Bitch' Tyga On Social Media Over Child Support!!
text:
3/29/2017 9:34 AM ET | Filed under: Celebrity Feuds • Business Blitz • Rob Kardashian • Celeb Kidz • Baby Momma Drama • Kylie Jenner • Dysfunctional Families • Tyga • Shade • Blac Chyna • Snapchat 
Tyga is in BIG trouble with his ex and baby momma! 
Seemingly out of nowhere, Blac Chyna went off on the rapper in a very public (and NSFW) Snapchat rant early Wednesday morning! 
This tea is hot, Perezcious readers!! 
Related: Tyga Says King Already Likes "Cars, Women & Jewelry" 
Not only did she slam Tyga AKA Michael Ray Nguyen-Stevenson for airing out her business with their son, King , but she claims he hasn't paid his child support either. Sh t! 
As we've previously reported, the KUWTK guest star has had his own money problems, including unpaid bills and lawsuits . 
You can read all her messages about her "bitch" ex, and even see how she pulled Kylie Jenner and Rob Kardashian into it by checking out the post (below). 
From left to right, Chyna wrote: 
It sounds like the momma of two is suggesting the 27-year-old makes less money than her AND has been talking about their son's bank account?? 
Regardless, something is definitely going down between the former flames! 
Chyna also included the address to her Lashed salon in California, so we can only wonder if she's telling Tyga to stop by so they can work things out in person… 
Considering they've had custody drama in the past over their four-year-old, we really hope they figure this whole drama out! 
Anyway, ch-ch-check out the 28-year-old reality TV star's Snapchat shade in full by flipping through the gallery (above)!
